{"success": true, "message": "Fetched question.", "data": {"showTimer": true, "showAttemptInsight": true, "playSounds": true, "dontShowCorrectAnswerImmediately": false, "_id": "648b5a64417cc3fb48d65ff9", "type": "singleCorrect", "level": 3, "category": null, "approximateTimeRequired": 180, "imageBaseUrl": null, "helperText": null, "source": "EM", "classes": [], "exams": ["615d76b2c52ffa3c944600df"], "subjects": ["615d708dbd4a37c4058ee5a8"], "chapters": ["615d6fed2b295b085ab6eba3"], "topics": [], "concepts": [], "microConcepts": [], "questionLabels": [], "previousYearPapers": [{"_id": "648b5a3a0d9d0b909f7b6488", "title": "JEE Main 2016 (03 Apr)", "isVisible": true}], "question": {"text": "The box of a pin hole camera, of length L, has a hole of radius a. It is assumed that when the hole is illuminated by a parallel beam of light of wavelength <math><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">&#955;</mi></math> the spread of the spot (obtained on the opposite wall of the camera) is the sum of its geometrical spread and the spread due to diffraction. The spot would then have its minimum size (say <math><msub><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">n</mi></mrow></msub></math> ) when:", "image": null}, "options": [{"id": "uax40", "text": "<math><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></msqrt></math> and <math><msub><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></msqrt></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": true}, {"id": "unnKt", "text": "<math><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>  and  <math><msub><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>4</mn><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></msqrt><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u00a0</mi></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "ZYjEH", "text": "<math><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mrow><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></mrow></mfrac></math>  and  <math><msub><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfenced separators=\"|\"><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}, {"id": "qcNga", "text": "<math><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">a</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></msqrt></math>  and  <math><msub><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">b</mi></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">m</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">n</mi></mrow></msub><mo>=</mo><mfenced separators=\"|\"><mrow><mfrac><mrow><mn>2</mn><msup><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">\u03bb</mi></mrow><mrow><mn>2</mn></mrow></msup></mrow><mrow><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">L</mi></mrow></mfrac></mrow></mfenced></math>", "image": null, "isCorrect": false}], "correctValue": null, "solution": {"text": "<p>In diffraction, first minima, we have</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>sin</mi><mi>&#952;</mi><mo>=</mo><mfrac><mi>&#955;</mi><mi>a</mi></mfrac></math></p><p><img src=\"https://cdn-question-pool.getmarks.app/pyq/jee_main/0406c97a-4bbf-4287-8dfc-30127e8a1cf5-image.png\" style=\"width: 200px; height: 185px;\" /></p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mi>b</mi><mo>=</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>+</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>L</mi><mi>&#955;</mi></mrow><mi>a</mi></mfrac><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>.</mo><mo>.</mo><mo>.</mo><mfenced><mi mathvariant=\"normal\">i</mi></mfenced></math></p><p>Then, minimum size of a spot, we get</p><p><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mfrac><mrow><mo>&#8706;</mo><mi>b</mi></mrow><mrow><mo>&#8706;</mo><mi>a</mi></mrow></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&#8658;</mo><mn>1</mn><mo>-</mo><mfrac><mrow><mi>L</mi><mi>&#955;</mi></mrow><msup><mi>a</mi><mn>2</mn></msup></mfrac><mo>=</mo><mn>0</mn><mo>&#8658;</mo><mi>a</mi><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi>&#955;</mi><mi>L</mi></msqrt><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>&#160;</mo><mo>.</mo><mo>.</mo><mo>.</mo><mfenced><mi>ii</mi></mfenced></math></p><p>So,</p><p>&nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><msub><mi>b</mi><mi>min</mi></msub><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mi>&#955;</mi><mi>L</mi></msqrt><mo>+</mo><msqrt><mi>&#955;</mi><mi>L</mi></msqrt></math></p><p>&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;<math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><mn>2</mn><msqrt><mi>&#955;</mi><mi>L</mi></msqrt></math><math xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML\"><mo>=</mo><msqrt><mn>4</mn><mi>&#955;</mi><mi>L</mi></msqrt></math>&nbsp;</p>", "image": null}, "videoSolution": null, "masterId": "MOGJMPYQ66978999", "numericalLowerLimit": null, "numericalUpperLimit": null, "bucket": "", "isRemoved": false, "cpyqbSubjects": ["61bb58181213731910ea0b70", "61c055eae8ce0dc8a5c62d33", "616057750283de43c87e3e1b", "61964fe0a5a5260118868021", "61964f81a5a526011886801d", "629f39e4ac11b26562e0625b", "616057920283de43c87e3e1e", "615f0c729476412f48314dab", "61a8a2c2e8ce0dc8a5c62d2d", "629105adee9e3ae00d63352b", "629f385f263330a77be9fa7d", "616056cd0283de43